⚠️ Psst... ⚠️ MUST READ to the end! 👀
Loungers, ALL TOGETHER NOW... 📢🙋‍♀️👯‍♀️ 
Goodbye 2020 -
Hello 2️⃣0️⃣2️⃣1️⃣! 👋
At a time that’s traditionally met with celebration and excitement, it seems like this year feels a little... different, right!? 🤷‍♀️
You might be feeling a little blue or a bit apprehensive to see what 2021 brings, but know this... 
💁‍♀️ You are not alone. We're with you - always. Our Female Family 💪
Throughout January, we'll be right here, filling your feeds with positivity and words of Lounge wisdom to see you through the month, and year, ahead! 
Now is the time to uplift each other girls. United around the world, LET'S LIGHT UP! ✨🌍
✋ Tag someone who NEEDS to see this and light them up!
✋ Tell them, and yourself, to TUNE IN TOMORROW at 7PM GMT 🕖 for something very, VERY EXCITING! 
Something BIG is coming! 👀🙌
Together, let's Light Up with Lounge. #lightupwithlounge

8 minutes and 46 seconds; the time it took to change the world as we know it.
Today marks exactly 2 weeks since George Floyd’s unjust and tragic murder. A murder which ignited the world and pushed the conversation about justice, representation and identity to the front of everyone’s minds. 
We ask you to take this time to think and reflect about everything that has happened, and how we can continue to make a stand for what is right. What can you do to ensure change is made… for the better, together?
People Made UNITED.
People Made ONE.
Change made TOGETHER.
Change made NOW.
We stand with you.
#BlackLivesMatter
#PeopleMadeChange
